{"tid":374121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港婚後玩Long distance","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T13:41:40.000Z","uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d152176d204113425284ac8ba4a1a261132a70","tid":374121,"uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"我同我老婆結咗婚一年左右 有個仔 <br />\n但因為我唔爭氣 所以我老婆都要翻工 <br />\n佢翻兩份工 一份朝九晚六 收咗工又要翻第二份 <br />\n我哋本身自己屋企都好遠 我住沙田佢住鰂魚涌 <br />\n所以佢一收工就直接翻屋企瞓 瞓醒又翻工 <br />\n我已經成個月無見過佢 <br />\n因為我都要翻工 所以個仔係我屋企人照顧住 <br />\n成日都好想見佢 我老婆已經一個月無翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純粹9up下 Sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}